    valuable:{name:"Increasingly valuable",read:"Your position combines hard-to-replicate assets with the ability to compound — exactly where advantage accrues as AI diffuses. Concentrate investment here and widen the gap while others are still catching up.",dot:"var(--sage)"},
    defensible:{name:"Defensible if strengthened",read:"You hold hard-to-replicate assets, but they aren't yet compounding. Add the learning loops and execution muscle that turn a static moat into a flywheel before rivals close the gap on capability.",dot:"var(--sage-mid)"},
    pressure:{name:"Under pressure",read:"You can improve quickly, but your advantages are replicable with the same models your rivals have. Anchor to a proprietary asset — data, workflow, trust — before the race commoditizes your position.",dot:"var(--brass)"},
    eroding:{name:"Eroding fast",read:"Your current advantages are both easy to replicate and not yet compounding. This is the danger zone as AI diffuses: the task is reinvention around a defensible asset, not optimization of what you have.",dot:"#B4472E"}
