var INDUSTRY = {
    "Manufacturing":"In manufacturing, AI quickly commoditizes generic scheduling, quality inspection, and documented process know-how — anything a competitor can buy off the shelf. Durable advantage concentrates in your proprietary operational data (machine telemetry, yield and defect history) wired into closed-loop control, and in the service and aftermarket models built on it; value migrates from efficient production toward data-rich, self-optimizing operations.",
    "Engineering / Construction":"In engineering and construction, AI is compressing drafting, early-stage design exploration, estimating, and standards/spec retrieval—reducing the time and cost of the billable cognitive labor the model has traditionally relied on. However, these tasks are not eliminated; they are accelerated and increasingly automated within human-in-the-loop workflows, especially where liability is high. Competitive advantage is shifting toward firms that own proprietary project, cost, and as-built data; maintain strong safety and compliance records; and have established client trust in complex, high-risk environments. As a result, value is migrating away from hours billed and toward data leverage, reusable design systems, and outcome-based delivery models.",
    "Professional Services":"In professional services, AI is compressing the value of routine research, drafting, and first-pass analysis—weakening the traditional leverage model built on junior billable hours and information asymmetry. The impact is uneven across domains but consistently reduces the scarcity of baseline expertise. Advantage is shifting toward firms that combine proprietary methodologies, outcome-linked data, and senior judgment with AI-enabled workflows embedded in client operations. As a result, value is migrating away from headcount leverage toward codified IP, measurable outcomes, and durable, trust-based client relationships.",
    "Field Services":"In field services, AI is rapidly standardizing core operational functions such as dispatch, scheduling, and first-line diagnostics, reducing differentiation at the workflow level. Durable advantage increasingly comes from proprietary equipment data, longitudinal service histories, high-quality first-time-fix datasets, and the systematic capture of technician expertise as structured knowledge. As these data assets compound, switching costs rise through deeper system integration and embedded service relationships. As a result, value is shifting away from transaction-based truck rolls toward predictive, outcome-based service models, where providers are paid for uptime, performance, or risk reduction rather than individual service events.",
    "Distribution":"In distribution, AI is rapidly standardizing capabilities like demand forecasting, catalog search, and order processing, reducing differentiation at the operational layer. Durable advantage is shifting toward proprietary transaction and supplier data, network density, and deeply embedded procurement workflows within customer operations. As a result, value is gradually moving away from margin-on-volume models toward differentiated category intelligence, predictive insights, and data-driven value-added services.",
    "Supply Chain":"In supply chain, AI is rapidly commoditizing baseline capabilities like demand forecasting, route optimization, inventory planning, and shipment-status visibility — anything available off the shelf from the same software vendors every competitor uses. Durable advantage concentrates in proprietary network data (longitudinal supplier performance, lane-level cost and disruption history, order-to-delivery outcomes) wired into execution systems that act on it automatically, and in the density and trust of the supplier and carrier relationships behind that data. As a result, value is migrating away from moving goods at lowest cost per unit toward resilience-as-a-service: predicting disruption before it lands, re-planning autonomously, and committing to outcomes — service levels, lead-time reliability, risk reduction — that competitors without the data history cannot underwrite.",
    "Investor Services":"In investor services, particularly among private wealth management firms, AI is automating much of the operational backbone—document handling, client onboarding, reporting, and components of portfolio construction and financial planning—while remaining embedded in advisor-led, high-trust workflows across tax, retirement, and estate planning, where it enhances scenario modeling and insight generation but does not replace fiduciary judgment. Competitive advantage is concentrating in proprietary, longitudinal client and household data that enable integrated personalization, embedded compliance and fiduciary infrastructure that creates barriers to entry, and trusted advisor-client relationships that anchor distribution and retention. As a result, value is shifting away from commoditized processing toward integrated planning intelligence, governance systems that operationalize fiduciary responsibility across domains, and control of client relationships and assets; notably, AI enables smaller firms to compete more effectively by delivering institution-grade, multi-domain advice, accelerating niche data advantages, and combining high-touch service with AI-augmented insight.",
    "Healthcare":"In healthcare, AI is standardizing documentation, coding support, triage, and literature synthesis, compressing margins in traditional workflows. Competitive advantage is shifting to proprietary outcomes data, real-world model performance, and deep integration into EHR and care delivery. Regulatory capability, auditability, and clinician trust are becoming core assets. As payment models evolve, differentiation will come from improving outcomes and reducing variability—not increasing throughput.",
    "Higher Education":"In higher education, AI commoditizes routine content delivery, generic tutoring, and many administrative workflows by making them cheaper, more scalable, and widely accessible beyond institutional boundaries. As these functions become less differentiating, advantage shifts toward trusted credentialing and reputation, proprietary learning-outcome and learner-behavior data, high-quality human mentorship and accountability, and deep employer and alumni networks that link learning to real opportunities. Institutional value migrates from owning content and controlling access toward demonstrable outcomes, personalization that integrates human and AI support, and resilient communities of practice that learners and employers rely on as signals of quality and fit.",
    "Other":"Across the mid-market, AI is rapidly commoditizing routine cognitive work and standard software capabilities, reducing the value of tasks and tools that can be easily replicated. At the same time, it is increasing the importance of assets that are harder to copy: proprietary data, deeply embedded workflows, trusted relationships in high-stakes decisions, and favorable regulatory positioning. The strategic question is specific to your organization: which of your current advantages are becoming easier to replicate with AI, and which are becoming more defensible and valuable because of it?"
  };
  var state = { screen:"intro", company:"", industry:"", current:0, scores:new Array(Q.length).fill(null) };
  var $ = function(id){ return document.getElementById(id); };

  // ---------- navigation ----------
  function show(screen){ state.screen=screen; ["intro","quiz","results"].forEach(function(s){ $("screen-"+s).classList.toggle("hidden",s!==screen); }); $("topStep").textContent=screen==="quiz"?"Question "+(state.current+1)+" of "+Q.length:(screen==="results"?"Complete":""); window.scrollTo({top:0,behavior:"auto"}); }
  $("startBtn").addEventListener("click", function(){ state.company=$("company").value.trim(); state.industry=$("industry").value; state.current=0; show("quiz"); renderQuestion(); });
  $("backBtn").addEventListener("click", function(){ if(state.current===0){ show("intro"); return; } state.current--; renderQuestion(); });
  $("nextBtn").addEventListener("click", function(){ if(state.scores[state.current]===null) return; if(state.current===Q.length-1){ renderResults(); show("results"); return; } state.current++; renderQuestion(); });

  // education panel toggle
  $("learnToggle").addEventListener("click", function(){
    var open=$("learn").classList.toggle("open");
    $("learnBody").hidden=!open;
    this.setAttribute("aria-expanded", open?"true":"false");
  });

  // ---------- question render ----------
  function renderQuestion(){
    var i=state.current, q=Q[i];
    $("qPhase").textContent=q.phase;
    $("qCount").textContent=String(i+1).padStart(2,"0")+" / "+Q.length;
    $("qText").textContent=q.text;
    $("qMeasures").textContent="Measures: "+q.measures;
    $("progressBar").style.width=((i/Q.length)*100)+"%";
    $("topStep").textContent="Question "+(i+1)+" of "+Q.length;

    // education panel (reset to collapsed each question, then populate)
    $("learn").classList.remove("open");
    var lb=$("learnBody"); lb.hidden=true; $("learnToggle").setAttribute("aria-expanded","false");
    lb.innerHTML =
      '<p>'+q.lens+'</p>'+
      '<div class="split">'+
        '<div class="cell er"><span class="k">AI erodes</span><p>'+q.erodes+'</p></div>'+
        '<div class="cell du"><span class="k">AI strengthens</span><p>'+q.endures+'</p></div>'+
      '</div>'+
      '<div class="ex"><span class="k">In practice</span><span class="t">'+q.example+'</span></div>';

    var levelText={1:q.a[1],2:"In between — closer to the description above than below.",3:q.a[3],4:"In between — closer to the description above than below.",5:q.a[5]};
    var host=$("levels"); host.innerHTML="";
    host.classList.remove("fade"); void host.offsetWidth; host.classList.add("fade");
    for(var lvl=1;lvl<=5;lvl++){ (function(lvl){
      var btn=document.createElement("button");
      btn.className="lvl"+(lvl===2||lvl===4?" between":""); btn.type="button";
      btn.setAttribute("aria-pressed", state.scores[i]===lvl?"true":"false");
      btn.innerHTML='<span class="num">'+lvl+'</span><span class="txt">'+levelText[lvl]+'</span>';
      btn.addEventListener("click", function(){
        state.scores[i]=lvl;
        Array.prototype.forEach.call(host.children,function(c){ c.setAttribute("aria-pressed","false"); });
        btn.setAttribute("aria-pressed","true");
        $("nextBtn").disabled=false;
        $("nextBtn").innerHTML=(i===Q.length-1)?'See results <span class="arw" aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span>':'Next <span class="arw" aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span>';
      });
      host.appendChild(btn);
    })(lvl); }
    $("nextBtn").disabled=state.scores[i]===null;
    $("nextBtn").innerHTML=(i===Q.length-1)?'See results <span class="arw" aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span>':'Next <span class="arw" aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span>';
    $("backBtn").textContent=(i===0)?"\u2190 Exit":"\u2190 Back";
  }

  // ---------- radar ----------
  var CX=300, CY=250, R=180, N=Q.length, LR=R+22;
  function pt(i,val){ var ang=(-90+i*(360/N))*Math.PI/180; var r=(val/5)*R; return [CX+r*Math.cos(ang), CY+r*Math.sin(ang)]; }
  function ring(val){ var d=""; for(var i=0;i<N;i++){ var p=pt(i,val); d+=(i===0?"M":"L")+p[0].toFixed(1)+" "+p[1].toFixed(1)+" "; } return d+"Z"; }
  function poly(vals){ var d=""; for(var k=0;k<N;k++){ var p=pt(k,vals[k]); d+=(k===0?"M":"L")+p[0].toFixed(1)+" "+p[1].toFixed(1)+" "; } return d+"Z"; }
  function lowestIndex(s){ var lo=0; for(var i=1;i<s.length;i++){ if(s[i]<s[lo]) lo=i; } return lo; }
  function highestIndex(s){ var hi=0; for(var i=1;i<s.length;i++){ if(s[i]>s[hi]) hi=i; } return hi; }
  function buildRadar(scores){
    var svg='<svg viewBox="0 0 600 500" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="img" aria-label="Radar chart of readiness scores">';
    for(var g=1;g<=5;g++){ svg+='<path d="'+ring(g)+'" fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,'+(g===5?0.22:0.10)+')" stroke-width="1"/>'; }
    for(var i=0;i<N;i++){ var edge=pt(i,5); svg+='<line x1="'+CX+'" y1="'+CY+'" x2="'+edge[0].toFixed(1)+'" y2="'+edge[1].toFixed(1)+'" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.09)" stroke-width="1"/>';
      var ang=(-90+i*(360/N))*Math.PI/180, lx=CX+LR*Math.cos(ang), ly=CY+LR*Math.sin(ang), cos=Math.cos(ang);
      var anchor=cos>0.25?"start":(cos<-0.25?"end":"middle"); var lines=Q[i].label, dy=(Math.sin(ang)<-0.3?-(lines.length-1)*11:2);
      svg+='<text x="'+lx.toFixed(1)+'" y="'+(ly+dy).toFixed(1)+'" text-anchor="'+anchor+'" font-family="IBM Plex Mono, monospace" font-size="10.5" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.82)">';
      for(var L=0;L<lines.length;L++){ svg+='<tspan x="'+lx.toFixed(1)+'" dy="'+(L===0?0:12)+'">'+lines[L]+'</tspan>'; } svg+='</text>'; }
    for(var v=1;v<=5;v++){ var vp=pt(0,v); svg+='<text x="'+(vp[0]+6)+'" y="'+(vp[1]+3).toFixed(1)+'" font-family="IBM Plex Mono, monospace" font-size="8.5" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.30)">'+v+'</text>'; }
    svg+='<g id="dataLayer"><path d="'+poly(scores)+'" fill="var(--on-dark-sage-soft)" stroke="var(--on-dark-sage)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linejoin="round"/>';
    var lo=lowestIndex(scores);
    for(var m=0;m<N;m++){ var mp=pt(m,scores[m]); var isLow=(m===lo); svg+='<circle cx="'+mp[0].toFixed(1)+'" cy="'+mp[1].toFixed(1)+'" r="'+(isLow?4.5:3.2)+'" fill="'+(isLow?"#E0B24A":"var(--on-dark-sage-dot)")+'" stroke="'+(isLow?"#E0B24A":"var(--on-dark-sage)")+'" stroke-width="1"/>'; }
    svg+='</g></svg>'; return svg;
  }

  // ---------- moat matrix ----------
  function buildMatrix(replic, compound){
    // replic (1-5, high = hard to replicate), compound (1-5, high = compounds)
    var x0=64,y0=16,s=300, W=x0+s+16, Ht=y0+s+52;
    var fracEasy=(5-replic)/4, compoundN=(compound-1)/4;
    var px=x0+Math.max(0.04,Math.min(0.96,fracEasy))*s;
    var py=y0+(1-Math.max(0.04,Math.min(0.96,compoundN)))*s;
    var hard=replic>=3, comp=compound>=3;
    var mx=x0+s/2, my=y0+s/2;
    function qfill(cx,cy){ return '<rect x="'+cx+'" y="'+cy+'" width="'+(s/2)+'" height="'+(s/2)+'" fill="var(--sage-tint)"/>'; }
    var svg='<svg viewBox="0 0 '+W+' '+Ht+'" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="img" aria-label="Moat matrix">';
    var hx = hard? x0 : mx, hy = comp? y0 : my;
    svg+=qfill(hx,hy);
    svg+='<rect x="'+x0+'" y="'+y0+'" width="'+s+'" height="'+s+'" fill="none" stroke="var(--line)" stroke-width="1.2"/>';
    svg+='<line x1="'+mx+'" y1="'+y0+'" x2="'+mx+'" y2="'+(y0+s)+'" stroke="var(--line)" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4 4"/>';
    svg+='<line x1="'+x0+'" y1="'+my+'" x2="'+(x0+s)+'" y2="'+my+'" stroke="var(--line)" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4 4"/>';
    function qlab(txt,cx,cy,active){ var col=active?"var(--sage-deep)":"var(--muted)"; var parts=txt.split("|");
      var out='<text x="'+cx+'" y="'+cy+'" text-anchor="middle" font-family="IBM Plex Mono, monospace" font-size="10" font-weight="'+(active?"500":"400")+'" fill="'+col+'">';
      for(var i=0;i<parts.length;i++){ out+='<tspan x="'+cx+'" dy="'+(i===0?0:13)+'">'+parts[i]+'</tspan>'; } return out+'</text>'; }
    svg+=qlab("Increasingly|valuable", x0+s/4, y0+s/4-4, hard&&comp);
    svg+=qlab("Under|pressure", x0+3*s/4, y0+s/4-4, !hard&&comp);
    svg+=qlab("Defensible if|strengthened", x0+s/4, y0+3*s/4-4, hard&&!comp);
    svg+=qlab("Eroding|fast", x0+3*s/4, y0+3*s/4-4, !hard&&!comp);
    svg+='<text x="'+(x0)+'" y="'+(y0+s+22)+'" font-family="IBM Plex Mono, monospace" font-size="9" fill="var(--muted)">Hard to replicate</text>';
    svg+='<text x="'+(x0+s)+'" y="'+(y0+s+22)+'" text-anchor="end" font-family="IBM Plex Mono, monospace" font-size="9" fill="var(--muted)">Easy to replicate</text>';
    svg+='<text x="'+(x0+s/2)+'" y="'+(y0+s+40)+'" text-anchor="middle" font-family="IBM Plex Mono, monospace" font-size="9" letter-spacing="0.12em" fill="var(--sage)">EASE OF REPLICATION WITH AI &#8594;</text>';
    svg+='<text transform="translate('+(x0-42)+','+(y0+s)+') rotate(-90)" font-family="IBM Plex Mono, monospace" font-size="9" fill="var(--muted)">Static</text>';
    svg+='<text transform="translate('+(x0-42)+','+(y0)+') rotate(-90)" text-anchor="end" font-family="IBM Plex Mono, monospace" font-size="9" fill="var(--muted)">Compounds</text>';
    svg+='<text transform="translate('+(x0-28)+','+(y0+s/2)+') rotate(-90)" text-anchor="middle" font-family="IBM Plex Mono, monospace" font-size="9" letter-spacing="0.12em" fill="var(--sage)">ABILITY TO COMPOUND &#8594;</text>';
    svg+='<g id="matMark"><circle cx="'+px.toFixed(1)+'" cy="'+py.toFixed(1)+'" r="9" fill="var(--sage)" fill-opacity="0.18"/>';
    svg+='<circle cx="'+px.toFixed(1)+'" cy="'+py.toFixed(1)+'" r="5" fill="var(--sage)" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="1.5"/>';
    var tx=px+ (fracEasy>0.7? -12:12), tAnchor= fracEasy>0.7?"end":"start";
    svg+='<text x="'+tx.toFixed(1)+'" y="'+(py-11).toFixed(1)+'" text-anchor="'+tAnchor+'" font-family="IBM Plex Mono, monospace" font-size="10" font-weight="500" fill="var(--sage-deep)">You</text></g>';
    svg+='</svg>'; return svg;
  }

  // ---------- results ----------
  function avg(idxs){ var s=0; for(var i=0;i<idxs.length;i++) s+=state.scores[idxs[i]]; return s/idxs.length; }
  function bandOf(sc){ return sc<=2?"low":(sc>=4?"high":"mid"); }
  function labelOf(i){ return Q[i].label.join(" ").replace(" / ","/"); }

  function renderResults(){
    var scores=state.scores.map(function(x){return x||1;});
    var overall=scores.reduce(function(a,b){return a+b;},0)/scores.length;

    $("rTitle").innerHTML = state.company ? '<span class="co">'+escapeHtml(state.company)+'</span> — AI strategic readiness' : "Your AI strategic readiness";
    var d=new Date(), months=["Jan","Feb","Mar","Apr","May","Jun","Jul","Aug","Sep","Oct","Nov","Dec"];
    $("rStamp").innerHTML = "Sagebridge · AI Advantage Loop<br>"+d.getDate()+" "+months[d.getMonth()]+" "+d.getFullYear();

var il=$("indLens");
    if(state.industry && INDUSTRY[state.industry]){
      $("indLabel").textContent = "Industry lens · " + state.industry;
      $("indText").textContent = INDUSTRY[state.industry];
      il.classList.remove("hidden");
    } else { il.classList.add("hidden"); }

    $("radarHolder").innerHTML = buildRadar(scores);
    var meLabel = state.company ? escapeHtml(state.company) : "This company";
    $("legend").innerHTML = '<span><i class="sw" style="border-top-color:var(--on-dark-sage)"></i>'+meLabel+'</span>';
    requestAnimationFrame(function(){ requestAnimationFrame(function(){ var dl=$("dataLayer"); if(dl) dl.classList.add("drawn"); }); });

    $("rScore").textContent=overall.toFixed(1);
    var band=BANDS[0]; for(var b=0;b<BANDS.length;b++){ if(overall>=BANDS[b].min) band=BANDS[b]; }
    $("rBand").textContent=band.name; $("rBandDesc").textContent=band.d;

    // phase cards
    var pc=$("phaseCards"); pc.innerHTML="";
    var phaseNames=Object.keys(PHASES);
    var phaseVals=phaseNames.map(function(p){ return {name:p, val:avg(PHASES[p].q)}; });
    var lowPhaseVal=Math.min.apply(null, phaseVals.map(function(x){return x.val;}));
    phaseVals.forEach(function(p){ var isLow=p.val===lowPhaseVal; var card=document.createElement("div"); card.className="pcard"+(isLow?" low":""); card.innerHTML='<div class="top"><span class="pn">'+p.name+'</span><span class="ps">'+p.val.toFixed(1)+'</span></div><div class="bar"><i style="width:'+((p.val/5)*100)+'%"></i></div>'; pc.appendChild(card); });

    // sharpest / strength
    var lo=lowestIndex(scores), hi=highestIndex(scores);
    $("focusTitle").textContent=labelOf(lo); $("focusText").textContent="Your lowest score ("+scores[lo]+"/5). "+Q[lo].move;
    $("strengthTitle").textContent=labelOf(hi); $("strengthText").textContent="Your highest score ("+scores[hi]+"/5). "+Q[hi].bands.high;

    // where the work lies
    var weakPhase=phaseVals.filter(function(x){return x.val===lowPhaseVal;})[0].name;
    $("synthTitle").textContent="Start with "+weakPhase+"."; $("synthText").textContent=PHASES[weakPhase].read;

    // moat matrix
    var replic=(scores[3]+scores[1])/2;   // proprietary assets + moat impact
    var compound=(scores[9]+scores[5])/2; // sense&adapt + capability
    $("matrixHolder").innerHTML=buildMatrix(replic,compound);
    requestAnimationFrame(function(){ requestAnimationFrame(function(){ var mm=$("matMark"); if(mm) mm.classList.add("shown"); }); });
    var hard=replic>=3, comp=compound>=3;
    var quad = hard&&comp?"valuable":hard&&!comp?"defensible":!hard&&comp?"pressure":"eroding";
    $("quadName").textContent=QUAD[quad].name; $("quadRead").textContent=QUAD[quad].read;
    var r2w=avg([3,4,5]), dot=$("r2wDot"), txt=$("r2wText");
    dot.style.background = r2w>=4?"var(--sage)":(r2w>=3?"var(--brass)":"#B4472E");
    txt.innerHTML = "<b>Right to win ("+r2w.toFixed(1)+"/5):</b> " + (r2w>=4?"within reach — you own defensible assets, see the prize, and can execute. Concentrate here.":(r2w>=3?"forming — but at least one of asset, prize, or capability needs work before you commit.":"not yet established — pin down which proprietary asset lets you capture a real prize first."));

    // dimension detail
    var det=$("detail"); det.innerHTML="";
    for(var i=0;i<Q.length;i++){
      var sc=scores[i], bnd=bandOf(sc);
      var card=document.createElement("div"); card.className="dcard";
      card.innerHTML =
        '<div class="dtop"><span class="dnum">'+(i+1<10?"0":"")+(i+1)+'</span>'+
        '<span class="dname">'+labelOf(i)+'</span>'+
        '<span class="dphase">'+Q[i].phase+'</span>'+
        '<span class="dchip '+bnd+'">'+sc+' / 5</span></div>'+
        '<div class="dinterp">'+Q[i].bands[bnd]+'</div>'+
        '<div class="dmove"><span class="k">To strengthen</span><span>'+Q[i].move+'</span></div>';
      det.appendChild(card);
    }

    // priorities: three lowest (ties broken by question order)
    var order=scores.map(function(s,i){return {i:i,s:s};}).sort(function(a,b){ return a.s-b.s || a.i-b.i; });
    var plan=$("plan"); plan.innerHTML="";
    for(var p=0;p<3;p++){ var it=order[p];
      var row=document.createElement("div"); row.className="prow";
      row.innerHTML='<div class="pn">'+(p+1)+'</div><div class="pc"><div class="pt">'+labelOf(it.i)+'<span class="sc">scored '+it.s+'/5 · '+Q[it.i].phase+'</span></div><div class="pd">'+Q[it.i].move+'</div></div>';
      plan.appendChild(row);
    }

    $("progressBar").style.width="100%";
  }

  function escapeHtml(s){ return s.replace(/[&<>"']/g,function(c){return {"&":"&amp;","<":"&lt;",">":"&gt;",'"':"&quot;","'":"&#39;"}[c];}); }

  $("printBtn").addEventListener("click", function(){ window.print(); });
  $("restartBtn").addEventListener("click", function(){ state.current=0; state.scores=new Array(Q.length).fill(null); $("company").value=state.company; if(state.industry) $("industry").value=state.industry; show("intro"); });
  $("company").addEventListener("keydown", function(e){ if(e.key==="Enter"){ $("startBtn").click(); } });

  show("intro");
})();
</script>
</body>
</html>
